==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Priceless
<hw>Price"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Too valuable to
admit of being appraised; of inestimable worth; invaluable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Of no value; worthless.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>J. Barlow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prick</ent>⟦br⟧
